# 💬 CryptoBuddy — AI-Inspired Cryptocurrency Chatbot 💰🚀

**CryptoBuddy** is a simple yet interactive **AI-inspired chatbot** that acts as your cryptocurrency companion.  
It provides instant responses to user queries about popular cryptocurrencies, including **price**, **trend**, and **market capitalization**.  

This project was developed as part of an **AI learning challenge** to demonstrate:
- **Conversational logic** using rule-based AI principles.
- **Frontend-Backend integration** using Python.
- **Interactive UI development** with **Streamlit**.

